11 accessible for individuals with disabilities.
12 An act relating to the creation of the Whole Home Repairs Program
13 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
14 Sec. 1. 10 V.S.A. § 700 is added to read:
15 § 700. VERMONT WHOLE HOME REPAIRS PROGRAM
16 (a) Creation of Program.
17 (1) The Department of Housing and Community Development shall
18 design and implement the Vermont Whole Home Repairs Program, through
19 which the Department shall award funding to statewide or regional nonprofit
20 housing organizations, or both, to provide competitive grants and forgivable
