12 Sec. 2. APPROPRIATION
13 The sum of $15,000,000.00 is appropriated from the General Fund to the
14 Department of Housing and Community Development in fiscal year 2026 for
15 the purposes of funding the Whole Home Repairs Program established in 10
16 V.S.A. § 700, $5,000,000.00 of which shall be used for technical assistance
17 and workforce development.
